data.description: Assumable VA loan at 2.5% interest. Seller will help with $$ closing cost assistance with acceptable offer.  Lovely all brick ranch home on a spacious corner lot in mid-town Newport News. Welcoming front porch to kick back and enjoy the wonderful weather in Southeastern Virginia. Great one level living with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The primary bedroom has an attached ensuite bath. Convenient to Christopher Newport University, military installations, the shipyard, shopping, dining, historic Williamsburg and Jamestown, and all the cultural and social diversity of the Peninsula area of Hampton Roads. Call to today to schedule your private tour.
